00:51:36,472 --> 00:51:36,933
I understand.

737
00:51:37,503 --> 00:51:42,505
All right, and listen, tell your husband I said good luck on the show.

738
00:51:42,525 --> 00:51:44,106
You don't know who my name is, do you?

739
00:51:44,126 --> 00:51:44,346
Okay.

740
00:51:44,406 --> 00:51:44,946
Yes, you do.

741
00:51:44,986 --> 00:51:45,086
Yes.

742
00:51:45,166 --> 00:51:45,527
All right now.

743
00:51:45,607 --> 00:51:48,088
Do we have anybody else on the call?

744
00:51:48,128 --> 00:51:48,248
No.

745
00:52:05,534 --> 00:52:06,435
